Name: Super Rocket Ride
About the game: Super Rocket Ride is a collaboration between Cosmocat and Unruly Games. It can best be described as a cross between old school lander games and classic platformers of the SNES era: a simple control scheme, lush pixel art, and unforgiving levels fraught with obstacles and hazards. Features Analog controls 33 hand-crafted levels Over-the-top physics-based deaths Contemporary atmospheric soundtrack featuring music from Snug, JFS and Ogotu
